💠 Believe you deserve all you have earned
💠 Believe you have the potential to be even more! 
You have the power... just believe 💠

node.text:
🧨 Legacy 🧨

Hold onto these moments... where you are a complete bad cat. There are enough reasons out there why you can’t or shouldn’t do something. 

Focus on the one that says you can! 

Remember how I’m paralyzed and strapped to my saddle? Nah... the clock doesn’t care either. 

You are enough. You are valuable. Your goals matter. You are a bad a$$! 

#amberleysnyder #walkriderodeo #frenchopen #legacyakalegs #rubybuckle

node.text:
❄️ French Open-Legacy ❄️

Came out on a mission at the @ruby_buckle to be 3rd in Round 1 and 3rd in the average! Big slip cost us in round 2 🙈 but my boy brought me nothing but smiles... and around $9500 🥰

#amberleysnyder #walkriderodeo #frenchopen #legacyakalegs 

Thank you to my team for getting us where we need to be!

node.text:
❤️ The time and effort put into this trailer is something I am thankful for every weekend I have been on the road!! 🛣

From the beautiful  details inside the living quarters to the accessible Smart Tack outside this trailer makes me smile daily! 

Just a little shout out to @harttrailer and @signaturequarters for giving me this place I’m currently laying in to make this post!! 😆 

#amberleysnyder #walkriderodeo #harttrailer #signaturequarters

node.text:
💢 Cheyenne Frontier Days 💢

The Daddy of em All! Not the run we planned on, woulda made it back if we had not tipped (a little hunty on first), but can you believe it?! We finally ran at this rodeo! 

To be the only paralyzed barrel racer in the United States does not give me my own category! We run with the best of the best going down that alley! I am so thankful to have this horse, my team, my family and my faith! ✝️ To live this life is not easy... but it is so worth it! 

#amberleysnyder #walkriderodeo
